lse,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: He said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, a man loves a people, but he cannot do good deeds like they do.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou, O Abu Dharr, will be with those you love.\u201d Abu Dharr said, \u201cI love Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22619,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/15\/dawud-strive-land-nashihah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23239,"position":4},"title":"David on Hikmah: How do I strive in the land with good will?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Abdul Aziz reported: The Prophet David, peace be upon him, said, \u201cO Lord, how do I strive for you in the land with good will?\u201d Allah said, \u201cRemember me often, love those who love me whether they are black or white, judge people as you would judge yourself,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3855,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/love-surah-ikhlaas-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23239,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Love for Surat al-Ikhlas leads to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I love this chapter, 'Say: He is Allah, the One,'\" (112:1). The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYour love for it will admit\u00a0you into Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 774 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u00a0Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/23239","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=23239"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/23239\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=23239"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=23239"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=23239"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}